# VEHICLE::SET_DISABLE_VEHICLE_ENGINE_FIRES

## Summary
Disable a MISSION vehicle from starting an engine fire

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle
* **BOOL** val

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
